title: Bugfix:
message:
Bugfix:
onsong format may contain chordpro tags (see https://onsongapp.com/docs/features/formats/chordpro/ )
if chordpro tags were used in a onsong file it was treated as a chordpro file instead of onsong.
If .onsong is part of the filename, do not try to detect other formats.

title: Transpose of Do-Ré-Mi chords now included (for fixed-Do scale)
message:
Transpose of Do-Ré-Mi chords now included (for fixed-Do scale)
Scaling of comment lines and song headings now available from 'Change fonts' menu
Deleting of multiple sets at once now allowed
Bible verses can now be imported into sets (requires internet access - via BibleGateway.com)
Fixed import of songs from Chordie.com
Fixed autoscroll predelay causing app to freeze for the duration of the predelay on some devices

title: Added new instruments for chord diagrams - cavaquinho, 4 and 5 string banjo
message:
Added new instruments for chord diagrams - cavaquinho, 4 and 5 string banjo
Updated ost_logo to rounded corners
Updated translations

title: Improved autoscroll length, also shows progress of autoscroll.
message:
Improved autoscroll length, also shows progress of autoscroll.
Page icons are now switched to the right (can be moved to the bottom as well).
Improved the transpose mode to show new key (if song key has been set).
Preferred keys can now be set (e.g. G# or Ab).
Preferred keys now use sharps or flats as appropriate.
Added other song fields to the search (copyright, ccli, aka, alttheme, user1, user2, user3).
Multiple sets can now be loaded at once - allowing the merging of sets.  The order they are selected in is the order they are loaded in.
Updated translations.
